{"id": 225014772, "title": "Marks & Spencer's 'very flattering' jumpsuit that makes you look 'years younger", "text": "Marks and Spencer has dropped a jumpsuit that's perfect for transitioning from spring into summer - and shoppers are heaping praise on it. A wonderfully versatile piece, the White Stuff's Jersey Drawstring Sleeveless Jumpsuit has been given a five-star rating by several reviewers online, with some saying it has the \"perfect\" fit. Costing \u00a355, the breezy style is made from organic cotton jersey with a drawstring that cinches you in the waist, a deep V-neck and sleeveless design. It also has cuffs at the ankles and pockets on either side. Available in either black or green, this jumpsuit is ideal for throwing on over T-shirts during the warm season. What's more is that it can be easily layered up when the weather turns. Simply add your favourite faux-leather biker jacket or a smart blazer. READ MORE: I'm an M&S fan and here's all you need to know about the \u00a330 summer beauty bag worth \u00a3170 Over on the M&S website, the Jersey Drawstring Sleeveless Jumpsuit has earned an incredible average rating of 4.8 from 21 reviews, so it's clearly a hit with shoppers. One happy customer, called Borderlaise, said: \"Love this jumpsuit! It\u2019s ideal for spring/ summer and goes with most tops. Really versatile and very flattering, it makes me look and feel 10 years younger!\" A second wrote: \"Comfortable to wear, easy to get in/out of. Can dress up or down. Much too long in leg so had to adjust straight away.\" While a third raved: \"This jumpsuit is slightly stretchy so it is very comfortable; it has a flattering shape.\" While most reviewers only had positive things to say about the jumpsuit, one person had a small issue, adding: \"The only thing I'm not keen on is the drawstring waist, so I will be taking it out and somehow trying to sew up the holes.\" The White Stuff Jersey Drawstring Sleeveless Jumpsuit is available for \u00a355 at marksandspencer.com. And right now, M&S customers who spend \u00a335 or more on on full-price beauty, clothing or homeware can snap up the retailer's new Summer Beauty Bag, which is worth \u00a3170, for just \u00a330. For those who don't mind splashing out, Nobody's Child sells a similar jumpsuit in three different colours - including black, white and denim-blue - for \u00a385. It has a wide-leg cut that skims the body.", "summary": "If you're looking for a flattering, versatile and comfortable jumpsuit, then you might want to check out this new-season Marks and Spencer item pronto", "url": "https://www.mirror.co.uk/money/shopping-deals/marks--spencers-very-flattering-32914815", "image": "https://i2-prod.dailyrecord.co.uk/lifestyle/fashion-beauty/article32884459.ece/ALTERNATES/s1200/0_MS.jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-05-29 12:44:08", "author": "Melisha Kaur,Melisha-kaur", "authors": ["Melisha Kaur", "Melisha-kaur"], "language": "en", "source_country": "gb", "sentiment": 0.448}